THE BEST IDEA,
SWEETIE.

14:06.500 --> 14:09.500
WHOO-WHOO-WHOO-WHOO!

14:09.500 --> 14:11.583
BOOK 'EM, DANNO.

14:11.583 --> 14:12.667
SO THIS IS WHAT IT'S LIKE

14:12.667 --> 14:15.000
WHEN THEY CART YOU OFF
TO PRISON, HUH?

14:15.000 --> 14:16.834
DEPENDS. THERE'S MORE
THAN ONE KIND OF PRISON.

14:16.834 --> 14:18.458
THERE ARE
THE STATE-REGULATED ONES,

14:18.458 --> 14:21.000
THEN ONES
YOU GET TRAPPED IN WHEN
YOUR LIFE IS GOING NOWHERE

14:21.000 --> 14:22.291
AND EVERYONE ELSE
SEEMS TO BE MOVING FORWARD.

14:22.291 --> 14:25.041
TOOK A HAPPINESS PILL
THIS MORNING, DID WE?

14:25.041 --> 14:27.500
NO, JUST A STRONG DOSE
OF BLEAK REALITY.

14:27.500 --> 14:30.000
NO OFFENSE,
BUT HAVE YOU NOTICED
MY ONLY BIRTHDAY PLANS

14:30.000 --> 14:31.708
ARE TO PLAY THIRD WHEEL
TO MY FRIEND AND HIS GIRLFRIEND?

14:31.708 --> 14:34.000
OK, LISTEN, BUDDY,

14:34.000 --> 14:35.458
ON ANY OTHER DAY
OF THE YEAR,

14:35.458 --> 14:37.667
I'D BE MORE
THAN HAPPY TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT THIS,

14:37.667 --> 14:39.333
BUT SEEING AS TODAY
IS YOUR BIRTHDAY,

14:39.333 --> 14:41.542
WHY DON'T WE TRY
AND CONCENTRATE ON
THE POSITIVES?

14:41.542 --> 14:42.667
HEY! STOP THE CAR!

14:42.667 --> 14:43.583
[TIRES SCREECH]

14:43.583 --> 14:45.291
WHAT? WHAT?
WHAT DID WE HIT?

14:45.291 --> 14:48.041
NOTHING. JUST MAKE A U-TURN.
I SAW A REALLY COOL PLACE
BACK THERE.

14:50.959 --> 14:52.375
OK, UH...

14:52.375 --> 14:53.542
ANDIE...

14:53.542 --> 14:55.208
COULD WE PLEASE KEEP
THIS IMPULSIVE STREAK

14:55.208 --> 14:57.041
THAT YOU'RE TRYING
TO INDULGE TONIGHT

14:57.041 --> 14:59.166
FROM KILLING EVERYBODY
IN THIS CAR? PLEASE, HONEY?

14:59.166 --> 15:01.041
UH...DOCTOR'S ORDERS.

15:01.041 --> 15:02.041
REMEMBER, PACEY?

15:02.041 --> 15:03.708
YOU PROMISED I COULD
CUT LOOSE TONIGHT.

15:03.708 --> 15:06.750
YES, I DID,
DIDN'T I?

15:06.750 --> 15:07.417
MM-HMM.

15:07.417 --> 15:10.458
OK.

15:31.458 --> 15:32.667
OH, MY GOD.

15:32.667 --> 15:34.291
I MEAN, JACK,
YOU LOOK AMAZING.

15:34.291 --> 15:37.000
WOW, IT'S LIKE
THE TRANSFORMATION
FROM JOHN-BOY TO JOHN-JOHN

15:37.000 --> 15:39.834
WAS ALL IN A JAR
OF DIPPITY-DOO.

15:39.834 --> 15:41.000
IT'S NO BIG DEAL.
I PUT A LITTLE GEL IN MY HAIR.

15:41.000 --> 15:43.458
THAT'S PRETTY MUCH
THE EXTENT OF IT.

15:43.458 --> 15:46.542
