YOU GET STYLE.

15:46.542 --> 15:50.375
I WISH I HAD NABBED YOU
ONE SEXUAL PREFERENCE
AGO.

16:02.375 --> 16:03.917
HELLO, TY.

16:03.917 --> 16:04.959
EXCELLENT.

16:04.959 --> 16:06.333
[GIGGLES]
YOU'RE LEARNING.

16:06.333 --> 16:07.417
UH-HUH.

16:07.417 --> 16:08.125
MMM.

16:14.625 --> 16:16.000
OK.

16:16.000 --> 16:17.417
EXPLANATION.

16:17.417 --> 16:18.875
WHAT?

16:18.875 --> 16:21.458
WELL, FIRST THIS MORNING
AND THEN RIGHT NOW,

16:21.458 --> 16:23.792
THAT'S 2 KISSES THAT YOU'VE
BAILED OUT ON TODAY.

16:23.792 --> 16:27.750
OK, IT'S JUST THAT
WE'VE BEEN GETTING
CLOSER, YOU KNOW?

16:27.750 --> 16:29.708
I KNOW,
IT'S CALLED DATING.

16:29.708 --> 16:32.250
I REALIZE THAT,
BUT WHEN DOES IT STOP?

16:34.875 --> 16:36.375
YOU'RE KIDDING, RIGHT?

16:36.375 --> 16:39.708
JEN, UH, YOU...

16:42.000 --> 16:43.458
YOU TURN ME ON.

16:43.458 --> 16:47.708
AND THE CLOSER WE GET,
THE MORE YOU TURN ME ON.

16:47.708 --> 16:49.417
IS THAT SUCH A BAD THING?

16:49.417 --> 16:51.000
A-ALL I'M SAYING IS

16:51.000 --> 16:53.959
IS THAT IT'S POSSIBLE
THAT THINGS COULD GET
OUT OF HAND.

16:53.959 --> 16:56.333
REALLY?

16:58.041 --> 16:59.458
HOW OUT OF HAND?

16:59.458 --> 17:00.625
LOOK, I'M SERIOUS.

17:00.625 --> 17:02.000
WE'VE BARELY MADE OUT,

17:02.000 --> 17:04.791
AND YOU'RE ALREADY
WORRIED ABOUT THINGS
GOING OUT OF HAND.

17:06.250 --> 17:07.165
IT'S SWEET.

17:07.165 --> 17:11.458
IN A VERY 1956
SORT OF WAY.

17:11.458 --> 17:12.165
OH, YEAH?

17:12.165 --> 17:15.708
WELL, HOW 1956
IS THIS?

17:20.625 --> 17:23.583
[UPTEMPO BLUES PLAYING]

17:26.416 --> 17:28.875
WHOA. WHO ARE YOU,

17:28.875 --> 17:30.041
AND WHAT
HAVE YOU DONE
WITH MY GIRLFRIEND?

17:30.041 --> 17:32.041
SHE'S BEEN HERE ALL ALONG.

17:32.041 --> 17:37.708
JUST TRAPPED BENEATH
THE BONDAGE OF GAP CLOTHING
AND A GOOD-GIRL COMPLEX.

17:37.708 --> 17:41.208
WHY,
THE GOOD-GIRL COMPLEX
WAS PART OF YOUR CHARM.

17:41.208 --> 17:43.250
PART  OF MY CHARM.

17:43.250 --> 17:44.583
NOT ALL OF IT.

17:44.583 --> 17:45.834
REMEMBER, WE'RE HAVING FUN.

17:45.834 --> 17:50.083
BESIDES, MARLIE SAID I HAVE
TO LEARN TO LET MY ID OUT

17:50.083 --> 17:52.208
TO BREATHE SOME FRESH AIR
FOR AN EVENING.

17:52.208 --> 17:56.125
WHAT EXACTLY ARE YOU LETTING
OUT FOR AN EVENING?

17:56.125 --> 17:58.041
IT'S WHAT FREUD
CALLS YOUR ID.

17:58.041 --> 18:02.875
IT'S THE PART OF YOU
THAT HOLDS YOUR PUREST
IMPULSES AND DESIRES.

18:02.875 --> 18:06.041
AND IT DOESN'T JUDGE OR
CARE WHAT ANYONE THINKS,

18:06.041 --> 18:07.166
IT JUST...
WANTS WHAT IT WANTS.

18:07.166 --> 18:08.875
AND WHAT DO YOU
THINK IT WANTS?

18:08.875 --> 18:13.417
WELL, IT'S ABOUT
LETTING GO OF ALL
YOUR PRECONCEIVED NOTIONS

18:13.417 --> 18:15.959
OF HOW YOU'RE
SUPPOSED TO TALK

18:15.959 --> 18:18.417
OR HOW YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BEHAVE AND...

18:18.417 --> 18:19.708
JUST LETTING LOOSE
FOR ONCE.

18:19.708 --> 18:23.500
I COULD CERTAINLY
LEARN SOMETHING
ABOUT LETTING LOOSE.

18:23.500 --> 18:26.667
LOOK AT ME, I'M SITTING
IN A BAR, I'M DRINKING
A STRAIGHT COKE.

18:26.667 --> 18:28.875
WELL, WE COULD DO IT
TOGETHER, IF YOU WANT.

18:28.875 --> 18:33.875
I MEAN, IT MIGHT BE GOOD
FOR BOTH OF US TO GET
A LITTLE WILD TONIGHT.

18:35.125 --> 18:37.208
JUST TRY NOT
TO GET TOO WILD

18:37.208 --> 18:38.834
WHILE I'M AWAY
AT THE WASHROOM, OK?

18:40.250 --> 18:42.083
CAN I GET YOU GUYS
ANYTHING ELSE?

18:42.083 --> 18:43.750
UH, YEAH.

18:43.750 --> 18:45.417
I'LL HAVE ANOTHER COKE,

18:45.417 --> 18:47.458
AND COULD YOU TELL
THE BARTENDER

18:47.458 --> 18:50.625
TO PUT A LITTLE MORE RUM
IN IT THIS TIME?

18:50.625 --> 18:53.583
YEAH, ME, TOO. I CAN BARELY
EVEN TASTE THE RUM IN MINE.

18:53.583 --> 18:55.333
OH, SORRY ABOUT THAT.

18:55.333 --> 18:58.083
I'LL HAVE HIM DOUBLE
THE SHOTS IN THE NEXT ROUND
TO MAKE UP FOR IT.

18:58.083 --> 18:59.291
THANK YOU.

18:59.291 --> 19:00.291
YAAGH!

19:00.291 --> 19:01.583
HAVE YOU EVER DRANK
BEFORE?

19:01.583 --> 19:03.875
NEVER.
ME, NEITHER!

19:09.000 --> 19:11.959
SO, HOW DOES IT FEEL
TO BE THE ONE

19:11.959 --> 19:13.125
WHO SET THIS LITTLE
HAMLET ON ITS EARS?

19:13.125 --> 19:15.917
