TALKING TO ME?

19:15.917 --> 19:17.917
I DON'T LIKE YOU, ABBY.

19:17.917 --> 19:20.208
WELL, THAT'S 'CAUSE
NO ONE LIKES ME.

19:20.208 --> 19:21.792
I'M AN OUTCAST.
WELCOME TO THE CLUB.

19:21.792 --> 19:24.083
HEH.

19:24.083 --> 19:27.208
