IS JUST SO RIDICULOUS.

19:27.208 --> 19:29.458
THERE'S NO SUCH THING
AS GAY, ANYWAY.

19:29.458 --> 19:33.041
JUST THIS WEIRD LABEL
PEOPLE CAME UP WITH

19:33.041 --> 19:33.834
TO PERSECUTE
THE NORMAL INCLINATION

19:33.834 --> 19:36.291
TO GO BOTH WAYS.

19:37.750 --> 19:39.166
WHAT DO YOU--
WHAT YOU MEAN?

19:39.166 --> 19:42.333
WELL, WE'RE ALL BISEXUAL,
DON'T YOU THINK?

19:42.333 --> 19:44.375
WE'RE ALL JUST
SEXUAL ANIMALS
UNDER GOD.

19:44.375 --> 19:48.125
THIS PURITANICAL SOCIETY
WOULD MAKE YOU THINK

19:48.125 --> 19:51.083
OUR NATURAL IMPULSES ARE
SOMETHING TO BE ASHAMED OF.

19:51.083 --> 19:53.583
WHEN IT'S REALLY
THOSE KINDS OF ATTITUDES

19:53.583 --> 19:55.083
THAT ARE THE EMBARRASSMENT.

19:55.083 --> 19:56.792
