♪ FEVER IF YOU
LIVE AND LEARN... ♪

20:10.708 --> 20:11.750
HOW YOU GUYS DOING?

20:11.750 --> 20:13.417
I THINK WE'RE READY
FOR ANOTHER ROUND.

20:13.417 --> 20:14.708
SOUNDS GOOD TO ME.

20:14.708 --> 20:15.959
2 MORE COMING UP.

20:15.959 --> 20:18.625
HOW MANY COKES ARE YOU GUYS
GONNA SWILL TONIGHT?

20:18.625 --> 20:20.500
♪ WHAT A LOVELY WAY
TO BURN ♪

20:25.542 --> 20:29.000
WELL, ALL RIGHT.
