THE BEST IDEA,
DO YOU, SWEETHEART?

20:37.959 --> 20:39.333
SURE, IT IS.

20:40.875 --> 20:43.208
OH, BOY.

20:43.208 --> 20:44.500
GUYS, BLUES RIFF.

20:44.500 --> 20:45.959
YOU GOT IT.

20:52.375 --> 20:53.875
HEH HEH.

