24:03.125 --> 24:04.417
SO, WHAT DO YOU
WANNA DO NEXT?

24:04.417 --> 24:05.875
MMM...

24:05.875 --> 24:09.250
AHH...YOU GUYS HAVE
BEEN DRINKING.

24:09.250 --> 24:10.667
EXCUSE ME, WAITRESS.

24:10.667 --> 24:12.250
MAKE THIS ONE
A DOUBLE THIS TIME

24:12.250 --> 24:14.166
WITH JUST
A SPLASH OF COKE.

24:14.166 --> 24:16.417
ACTUALLY, YOU KNOW WHAT?
A SPLASH IS TOO MUCH.

24:16.417 --> 24:19.250
HOW ABOUT JUST A SPLA?
NO "SH" AT ALL.

24:19.250 --> 24:20.500
NO "SH." HEH HEH.

24:20.500 --> 24:22.625
BEFORE I BRING YOU
ANYTHING ELSE,

24:22.625 --> 24:25.041
THE BARTENDER ASKED ME
TO CHECK YOUR I.D.s.

24:25.041 --> 24:27.041
CHECK OUR I.D.s?

24:27.041 --> 24:29.166
OK, YOU SHOULD'VE
DONE THAT 5 DRINKS AGO,

24:29.166 --> 24:32.625
BECAUSE YOU KNOW WHAT?
WE ARE 16 YEARS OLD.

24:32.625 --> 24:34.250
NO, WE ARE.
AND YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:34.250 --> 24:35.708
YOU, LITTLE MISSY,
HAVE JUST BROKEN
THE LAW.

24:35.708 --> 24:38.041
YOU COULD LOSE
YOUR JOB OVER THIS.

24:38.041 --> 24:39.500
NOT ONLY COULD YOU
LOSE YOUR JOB,

24:39.500 --> 24:41.875
BUT YOU COULD LOSE
YOUR LIQUOR LICENSE.
YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:41.875 --> 24:44.542
THIS IS MY BOYFRIEND,
AND HIS FATHER
IS THE TOWN SHERIFF.

24:44.542 --> 24:45.959
DAWSON, NOW. UP, UP.
NOW. HELP ME OUT.

24:45.959 --> 24:48.667
HEY, LISTEN,
SHE'S KIDDING.
IT'S A JOKE.

24:48.667 --> 24:50.291
I'M NOT.
MY I.D.'s HERE.
WANNA SEE IT?

24:50.291 --> 24:51.792
I'LL SHOW IT TO YOU.
I'LL SHOW IT.

24:51.792 --> 24:55.250
WHAT ARE YOU THINKING,
HUH? 16 YEARS OLD.

24:59.708 --> 25:04.250
SO, I WAS OUT IN THE GARAGE.
SAW THE EXPLORER.

25:04.250 --> 25:05.041
VERY BEAUTIFUL.

25:05.041 --> 25:07.125
QUITE A GIFT.

25:07.125 --> 25:09.667
OF COURSE, I ALWAYS THOUGHT
THAT DAWSON'S FIRST CAR

25:09.667 --> 25:12.208
WOULD BE SOMETHING LIKE I HAD
WHEN I WAS A BOY, YOU KNOW,

25:12.208 --> 25:13.458
SOME OLD JALOPY
OR SOMETHING.

25:13.458 --> 25:16.500
OF COURSE,
IT'S YOUR DECISION.

25:16.500 --> 25:20.750
MMM. WELL, IT SEEMS THAT
A LOT OF THINGS THAT
CAME WITH THIS MARRIAGE

25:20.750 --> 25:22.291
ARE MY DECISION
THESE DAYS.

25:22.291 --> 25:26.125
EXCEPT, OF COURSE,
THE DECISION ABOUT
THE MARRIAGE ITSELF.

25:45.375 --> 25:47.458
OK, WE HAVE TO STOP.

25:47.458 --> 25:49.792
I CAN'T DO THIS.

25:55.083 --> 25:56.917
I'M SORRY, JEN.

25:56.917 --> 25:58.834
YOU SHOULD BE.

25:58.834 --> 26:02.041
WELL, IT'S NOT
ENTIRELY MY FAULT.

26:02.041 --> 26:05.542
OH, REALLY? WHAT ROLE
AM I PLAYING IN YOUR
PERSONAL INNER STRUGGLE?

26:05.542 --> 26:08.959
Y-Y-YOU'RE TEMPTING ME.

26:10.333 --> 26:12.041
